snippet.title: Do I Pass? Trailer
snippet.description:
A trailer for my gameboy game: Do I Pass?

In the game you are a trans woman who is worried about if she passes. She becomes a ghost to see how people gender her. 

Play it at:

https://taylormccue.itch.io/do-i-pass
